4%2c104%2c20220517%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CYDM,111,金訴,104,20220517,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"金訴","JNO":"104","JDATE":"20220517","JTITLE":"違反洗錢防制法等"}